===Etymology===
{{der|zh|sit}}. Cognate with {{cog|mro|tr=iu ~ ʔiu|t=dark}} ({{zh-ref|Löffler, 1966}}); possibly also related to {{cog|bo|གཡོག|t=to cover}} and {{m|bo|གཡོགས|t=lid}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Related to {{zh-l|黝}}, {{zh-l|窅}}, {{zh-l|杳}}, {{zh-l|穾}}, {{zh-l|窔}}.

Allofam is probably {{och-l|窈窕}} (ibid.).

